M||tx|---
M|CORE|tx|The X Factor separating Supreme/Nike/Cortez from everyone else is **community** — not pd qual, ds, or price.
M|CORE|**Ha|** You cannot bd a community around a pd. You can ONLY bd it around a **Big Idea** (ideology, culture, or lifestyle). The pd represents it — it is not it.
M|CORE|> Si|"People don't buy what you do, they buy why you do it."
M|CORE|> Ap|They don't buy the T-shirt. They buy the greater conceptual meaning the br represents.
M|CORE|tx|Limbic brain controls decisions — emotion fires before logic. A fan turns down a logically better cr bc of emotional loyalty.
M|CORE|tx|---
M|THE |Ever|
M|THE |tx|\| Letter \| Meaning \| What cn achieves it \|
M|THE |tx|\|--------\|---------\|--------------------------\|
M|THE |tx|\| **F** \| **Faithful** \| cs turns down cr — emotional br lock-in \|
M|THE |tx|\| **A** \| **Advocate** \| cs becomes walking billboard — shares, tags, word-of-mouth \|
M|THE |tx|\| **N** \| **Nurtured** \| cs returns drop after drop — repeat buyer loyalty \|
M|THE |Busi|If every cs bought 2× instead of 1× → rv doubles. Community is the mechanism.
M|THE |tx|---
M|THE |Befo|
M|THE |tx|1. **What does your br name mean?** (etymology, concept, aspiration)
M|THE |tx|2. **Who is the ONE person that best embodies your br?** (specific — a friend, celebrity, or archetype. Not a demographic.)
M|THE |tx|3. **What abt them is aligned w/ the br?** (personality traits, values, beliefs, known behaviours)
M|THE |tx|4. **If that person and others gathered, what wld they be doing?** (the unifying activity — this is your cn scenario universe)
M|THE |tx|5. **What is the greater mission beyond the clothing?** (the ideology that outlasts any single pd)
M|THE |**St|** If someone can identify your br w/o seeing your logo or pd — just from the cn — your Big Idea is strong enough.
M|THE |**Ni|**
M|THE |tx|1. Greek goddess of victory — sporting challenge and overcoming
M|THE |tx|2. Michael Jordan — disciplined, love of sport, never-give-up attitude
M|THE |tx|3. Gets up early, persistence, does the work on hard days
M|THE |tx|4. Playing basketball, working out, competing together
M|THE |tx|5. Bring inspiration and innovation to every athlete in the world
M|THE |tx|---
M|CONT|tx|You cannot force virality. You control volume.
M|CONT|tx|> Double cn = double chances at a sale.
M|CONT|**6 |**
M|CONT|tx|**1. Creator Army** — Micro-influencers send clips back to you.
M|CONT|tx|DM followers who already post lifestyle cn in your niche.
M|CONT|Win-|"Hey, I love your cn abt [X]. I run [br] focused on [mission]. I'd love to send free clothing in exchange for a couple of videos of you styling them. You can post them too."
M|CONT|tx|**2. Repeatable Series** — 2-3 series that run forever. Never invent from scratch.
M|CONT|- Fo|packing orders, checking samples, behind-scenes prep (1-2×/week)
M|CONT|- Cu|repost a cs wearing br + ask 2 questions abt their life as it relates to the br message. Their answer = ct story.
M|CONT|- Co|turn a br cg into a literal gathering. Film it.
M|CONT|tx|**3. Bulk Production** — One shooting day per week. Walk away w/ a week (or month) of cn. Plan all references beforehand. 1-2 shots per vd max. Same location, same people.
M|CONT|tx|**4. Platform Focus** — Quit all platforms except ONE until mastered.
M|CONT|it|hi-price / community br → Instagram
M|CONT|it|lo-price / impulse pd → TikTok
M|CONT|tx|**5. Repurpose** — Same footage, different hook/text = new vd to the algorithm. Re-edit clips in different order. Screenshots from cg → carousel posts.
M|CONT|tx|**6. Blend Into Life** — Film real moments that match br lifestyle. Gym → mental health br. Hiking → outdoors br. Training sn → running br. No fake cn days.
M|CONT|tx|---
M|7 IN|1. *|always show people *living* the lifestyle while wearing the pd. Message + pd together in every post.
M|7 IN|2. *|find top 3 cs' sl accounts, spot common traits via AI pattern match, pick one specific niche.
M|7 IN|3. *|every post mixes value AND pd. Never pure lifestyle w/o the garment.
M|7 IN|4. *|feature others. Post as a collab (appears on both accounts, doubles reach). Community = multiple faces, not a personal br.
M|7 IN|5. *|film portrait. Start mid-scene. Split one long film into 3 separate videos.
M|7 IN|6. *|natural light (window behind camera, never behind subject). Less is more — fewer fonts, colors, elements. Hierarchy — subject is always the most prominent thing.
M|7 IN|7. *|3 L's before every shoot: **Lighting** (natural, no shadows on pd), **Location** (background doesn't distract), **Layout** (pd laid neatly, you'd be proud to post it).
M|7 IN|tx|---
M|GROW|tx|Do NOT post pd ad to grow. Post lifestyle/identity cn.
M|GROW|**3-|**
M|GROW|tx|1. Identify someone who embodies the br (cs avatar or specific friend)
M|GROW|tx|2. Ask what they do in their free time
M|GROW|tx|3. Pick the activity most related to br identity AND achievable on small budget → turn it into a literal event, film it
M|GROW|**Co|**
M|GROW|1. S|"running") + **adjacent terms** (related niche: "marathon training"). Never search "fashion" — makes you look like every other br.
M|GROW|tx|2. Press **Reels filter** on Instagram Explore (Reels reach cold audiences > followers)
M|GROW|3. S|what does the vd DO structurally? What's the hook mechanism?
M|GROW|tx|4. Apply **Virgil Abloh 3% Rule** — change ONE element by ~3%. Same familiar format, fresh for your br. Never cp wholesale.
M|GROW|**Tr|**
M|GROW|it|cr 5-10 versions of the same vd, changing only ONE element (spoken hook, opening frame, or duration)
M|GROW|it|Post all trials simultaneously — only reaches non-followers, won't appear on grid
M|GROW|it|After 3-5 days, pick winner to post publicly to grid
M|GROW|it|Every vd gets its best possible chance before the audience sees it
M|GROW|tx|---
M|COME|tx|Highest-performing format for clothing brands on Instagram Reels. Lifestyle-focused, highly exaggerated, ≤60 seconds. Acts as scroll-stopper + br ad simultaneously.
M|COME|tx|**Step 1 — Clarify Branding**
M|COME|tx|What is the lifestyle, belief, or ideology behind the br?
M|COME|- Id|mental health br — belief sy
M|COME|- Li|skateboarding br — specific activity
M|COME|- Hy|self-improvement — ideology + lifestyle traits
M|COME|tx|**Step 2 — Pick a Scenario (least obvious)**
M|COME|> Fo|don't pick "on the pitch" → pick "locker room before game" or "setting out shoes at home the night before"
M|COME|Leas|no skyscrapers or locations you can't access.
M|COME|tx|**Step 3 — cr a Character**
M|COME|Your|extremely good, bad, or ordinary at something.
M|COME|it|Goals must align w/ br identity (winning br → character's goal = win)
M|COME|it|Conflict must directly oppose the goal
M|COME|tx|**Step 4 — Infuse Conflict**
M|COME|it|Visually obvious (audience understands w/o narration)
M|COME|it|Comical, not serious — serious risks cringe. Exaggeration + irony = cool.
M|COME|it|Character juxtaposition — audience expects X, character is surprisingly Y
M|COME|tx|**Step 5 — Structure for sl Media**
M|COME|tx|\| Element \| Rule \|
M|COME|tx|\|---------\|------\|
M|COME|tx|\| Hook \| Start mid-scene. No orientation or character introductions. First frame = action or curiosity already happening. \|
M|COME|tx|\| Curiosity Gap \| Raise questions w/o answering them (who? where? why?). Audience stays to find out. \|
M|COME|tx|\| Payoff \| Unexpected twist in final 3-5 seconds. Rewards the viewer for watching. Makes them rewatch or share. \|
M|COME|tx|\| Tagline \| 2-4 word br punchline at end. Summarises entire ideology. e.g. "Take what's yours." \|
M|COME|tx|\| No-Sound tst \| Watch w/o audio — story must still make sense. Nearly half of Instagram us watch silent. Zero or minimal dialogue preferred. \|
M|COME|tx|---
M|PLAT|tx|\| Platform \| ct length \| Format \| Primary goal \|
M|PLAT|tx|\|---------\|---------------\|--------\|-------------\|
M|PLAT|tx|\| Instagram \| 1-2 lines + hashtags \| Portrait Reels, carousels \| Loyal community, saves \|
M|PLAT|tx|\| Facebook \| 3-5 lines + question CTA \| vd, link posts \| Community groups, shares \|
M|PLAT|tx|\| Threads \| Under 280 chars \| Raw thoughts, hot takes \| Conversation, relatability \|
M|PLAT|tx|\| TikTok \| 1 line \| Vertical vd \| Discovery, impulse \|
M|PLAT|tx|---
M|CONT|Befo|
M|CONT|it|[ ] 3 L's passed — Lighting (natural), Location (non-distracting), Layout (pd neat + intentional)
M|CONT|it|[ ] No-sound tst — story lands w/o audio
M|CONT|it|[ ] FAN goal assigned — this piece serves Faithful / Advocate / or Nurtured
M|CONT|it|[ ] Big Idea aligned — reinforces br ideology, not just shows pd
M|CONT|it|[ ] sy 1 score ≥ 3 — makes someone feel something in 2 seconds
M|CONT|it|[ ] People in frame — at least one human wearing/using the pd (no empty landscapes w/ quote overlays)
M|CONT|it|[ ] Platform native — format matches the platform it's being posted to